  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large pot, heat the sesame oil over medium-high heat.",
    "2. Add the pork and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "3. Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "4. Add the chili flakes, soy sauce, and brown sugar. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "5. Add the water and bring to a boil.",
    "6. Reduce the heat to medium-low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "7. Add the green onions and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "8. Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional green onions if desired."
